Century 21 Big Sky Real Estate (2844) - Plains

data.description:
******$5,000 seller closing credit. Motivated seller!!*****
Cute 3 bed, 1 bath home with double car garage, detached shop and carport. This home has had some updates and the beautiful hardwood floors were refinished a few years ago with nearly no wear or tear! There are massive amounts of storage in this home, as well as in the garage and shop. With several fruit trees and a greenhouse, you'll be ready to grow your own food. The carport also allows for all of your vehicles and toys to be under cover. The backyard is completely fenced, along with a drive-through gate for easy access. There is an additional library/nursery/craft room off the master that could be what ever you dream it to be! With a working fireplace, this home is a great spot any time of the year. Located in the cute town of Plains, you are within walking distance of the schools, cute shops and hospital. Professional photos coming soon. Contact Tara Bowman at 406-250-8793 or your Real Estate Professional.
